{"tid":1653630,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"FreeHKLIve 反送中直播網，招募識任何外語嘅巴絲幫忙","createTime":"2019-10-14T07:25:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T16:50:02.000Z","uid":304470,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"6582d34f490c3f92f1d5ea9977f4a02f4d444484","tid":1653630,"uid":304470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:25:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/10/otPrsN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F10%2FotPrsN.png&h=f31113f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小弟幾個月前開始營運緊 <a href=\"https://freehk.live\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffreehk.live&d=JMO6Z0a0EEbNsRtkVA0DAlT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=43b3a18c\" target=\"_blank\">https://freehk.live</a><br />\n有見唔少外國人參與討論 / 收睇，所以希望提供一個具多國語言功能for外國人睇live。因為鬼佬未必識係facebook搵香港本地媒體嘅live黎睇，所以提供一個方便d既平台比鬼佬用都幾重要。<br />\n<br />\n現招募識任何一種外掛嘅巴絲幫手翻譯，任何一種外語都得 !<br />\n為免有三毛搞事，文件係read only:<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gi4VW8t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGi4VW8t.jpg&h=99b343d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果巴絲打有興趣幫手，請透過tg / facebook 搵我，我會將比編輯權限你入呢份文件 :<br />\ntg: <a href=\"https://t.me/nochinaextraditionforever\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fnochinaextraditionforever&d=JMO6Z0a0EEbNsRtkVA0DAlT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=52d6c348\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/nochinaextraditionforever</a><br />\nfb: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/freehklive\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffreehklive&d=JMO6Z0a0EEbNsRtkVA0DAlT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=0cc01ca6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/freehklive</a><br />\n<br />\n萬分感激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n香港人反抗 !</strong></span>"},{"pid":"267b708d24f363c1c9fc7873418eeb4bee981b27","tid":1653630,"uid":322141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:27:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c85b98d607ee546265ecb3f890253d3b096bd1d8","tid":1653630,"uid":304470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:30:20.000Z","msg":"小弟不才，英文版都可能需要搵人幫手執執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8a43b9d9dbd2c8fbce71df64651b62338f237f4","tid":1653630,"uid":7050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:34:09.000Z","msg":"我幫係推 <br />\n多謝各手足<br />\n但我中英都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好後悔無讀多d書"},{"pid":"3467ff1edb7ccba96192801efa92b81def8045c7","tid":1653630,"uid":304470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8a43b9d9dbd2c8fbce71df64651b62338f237f4","tid":1653630,"uid":7050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:34:09.000Z","msg":"我幫係推 <br />\n多謝各手足<br />\n但我中英都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好後悔無讀多d書"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:35:31.000Z","msg":"唔緊要，多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27d1617059594e59be516608a6f245542b627ab3","tid":1653630,"uid":69678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:40:52.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2480661f441a32027daa73962cc3c1f7bbdd68a","tid":1653630,"uid":39924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:42:41.000Z","msg":"幫你推"},{"pid":"3fd25a7132192fbc9839a5c398b49f0596fbdc40","tid":1653630,"uid":19005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:47